light/\" target=\"_blank\">Previous spotlights</a>','ROS Spotlight','','inherit','open','open','','268-autosave-v1','','','2014-04-23 21:10:33','2014-04-23 21:10:33','',268,'http://rosorg.osrfoundation.org/268-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
